@ECHO.
@ECHO Version 1.4 -- 4/2/2013
@ECHO.
@ECHO #############################################################
@ECHO.
@ECHO This script assumes the following values are true:
@ECHO.
@ECHO.
@ECHO ^* QT ^>^= 4.7.4 is installed at:
